WEBVTT

00:03:28.120 --> 00:03:30.056
Bulardan biri, shubhasiz, odamiylikdir.

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:31.880
u altruizmning asosi.

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:34.136
Biroq shunda savol o’zgaradi,

00:03:34.160 --> 00:03:36.920
bu xislat nega ba’zilarda ko’proq?

00:03:38.120 --> 00:03:42.016
Sababi altruist insonning miyasi 
boshqalarnikidan

00:03:42.040 --> 00:03:44.240
tubdan farqlanishida deyish mumkin.

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:47.016
Bunga oydinlik kiritish maqsadida,

00:03:47.040 --> 00:03:49.160
aslida ishni teskari, psixopatlarni

00:03:50.160 --> 00:03:51.360
o'rganishdan boshladim.

00:03:52.680 --> 00:03:55.776
Birovlarga yordam berish xislatini

00:03:55.800 --> 00:03:57.816
tushunishda qo’l keluvchi sodda yondashuv

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:00.976
bunday istakdan mahrum 
shaxslarni o'rganish